Package: powerPsych
Title: Effect Size and Power Toolbox for Psychologists 
Version: 0.0.0.9000.
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andrew",
           family = "Li",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "andrew-li@alumni.ubc.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This R package was developed for my STAT 545B course ath The University of British Columbia. This package has many tools that psychology researchers use. It has a calculator for effect size, power, sample size, and Cohen's d. Furthermore, it allows users to visualize Cohen's d.  
